<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29902>
    dc:description "Figures 70 - 74. Coleoscirus key illustrations. 70 Dorsal idiosomal shield with horizontal reticulations present 71 Gnathosoma with extensive reticulations present 72 a Sternal plate rounded posteriomedially, indentation absent 72 b Sternal plate rounded posteriomedially, indentation present 72 c Sternal plate truncated posteriomedially 73 a Dorsal idiosomal shield even sclerotized, light reticulation present 73 b Dorsal idiosomal shield unevenly sclerotized, light reticulation absent 74 a Integumental dots on legs forming rows 74 b Integumental dots on legs random." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29902" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

